00:00:46.730 --> 00:00:49.210
So what we've done so
far in this class is

00:00:49.210 --> 00:00:51.100
we've sort of said,
look, we've assumed

00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:53.020
whenever you make
decisions you make them

00:00:53.020 --> 00:00:55.390
with full knowledge
and full certainty.

00:00:55.390 --> 00:00:58.000
But many, many
decisions in life are

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.450
made under conditions
of uncertainty.

00:01:01.450 --> 00:01:02.890
So consider your
decision to study

00:01:02.890 --> 00:01:05.379
for the final in this class.

00:01:05.379 --> 00:01:09.310
In our models so far, you
